column2: SELECT n.objID, n.distance, n.type, p.ra AS pra, p.dec AS pdec, p.modelmag_r, pz.z as photoz FROM Galaxy AS G OUTER APPLY dbo.fCosmoComovDist2ObjectsRADEC (#, #, #, #, #, #, DEFAULT, DEFAULT, DEFAULT, DEFAULT, DEFAULT) as n LEFT JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON n.objid = p.objid LEFT JOIN Photoz as pz ON n.objid = pz.objid OUTER APPLY dbo.fCosmoComovDist2ObjectsRADEC (#, #, #, photoz, pra, pdec, DEFAULT, DEFAULT, DEFAULT, DEFAULT, DEFAULT) as n1 WHERE G.objID = n.objID HAVING n1< # INTO MyDB.NearbyObjEq5
